extendedInfo.description: The AFP International Conference on Fundraising has helped fundraising professionals around the world face a variety of challenges. For 2013, our goal is to engage and re-energize our industry, create balance, focus on critical priorities and simplify complexities. Join us at our 50th anniversary event and together we'll explore what it means to be DOING THE RIGHT THINGS, RIGHT!Keywords: AFP, Fundraising, Conference, ICON, San Diego, Philanthropy, Education
